Usually, from a historical study in the literature, the following information is available:


the design, eg, single-sequence drug-drug interaction (DDI), 2×2 BE, or 6×3 BE; 



the total sample size, N
0;



the 100(1 – 2α)% CI, (lower limit, upper limit), for the geometric mean ratio (GMR), T/R, of the PK parameters.
